StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: GETSENIORLECTURER
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.GETSENIORLECTURER(cSeniorLecturer OUT SYS_REFCURSOR)&lt;br/&gt;IS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; OPEN cSeniorLecturer FOR &lt;br/&gt; SELECT SeniorLecturer_table.idPerson, SeniorLecturer_table.surname, SeniorLecturer_table.firstName, &lt;br/&gt; SeniorLecturer_table.title, SeniorLecturer_table.address, SeniorLecturer_table.phone, SeniorLecturer_table.postcode,&lt;br/&gt; SeniorLecturer_table.campusLocation, SeniorLecturer_table.idBuilding, SeniorLecturer_table.numberOffice,&lt;br/&gt; SeniorLecturer_table.staffType, &lt;br/&gt; SeniorLecturer_table.area, SeniorLecturer_table.lectureType,SeniorLecturer_table.numberPhd, SeniorLecturer_table.numberMaster,&lt;br/&gt; SeniorLecturer_table.numberHonours&lt;br/&gt; FROM SeniorLecturer_table;&lt;br/&gt;END getSeniorLecturer;
